fields.name: ErrorDetails
fields.description: The errors that were encountered during execution of the operation. The details array contains the list of them.

fields.name: ExcludedPatchCount
fields.description: The number of patches that were not installed due to the user blocking their installation.

fields.name: FailedPatchCount
fields.description: The number of patches that could not be installed due to some issue. See errors for details.

fields.name: InstallationActivityId
fields.description: The activity ID of the operation that produced this result.

fields.name: InstalledPatchCount
fields.description: The number of patches successfully installed.

fields.name: LastModifiedDateTime
fields.description: The UTC timestamp when the operation finished.

fields.name: MaintenanceWindowExceeded
fields.description: Whether the operation ran out of time before it completed all its intended actions.

fields.name: NotSelectedPatchCount
fields.description: The number of patches that were detected as available for install, but did not meet the operation's criteria.

fields.name: OsType
fields.description: The operating system type of the machine.

fields.name: PatchServiceUsed
fields.description: Specifies the patch service used for the operation.

fields.name: PendingPatchCount
fields.description: The number of patches that were identified as meeting the installation criteria, but were not able to be installed. Typically this happens when maintenanceWindowExceeded == true.

fields.name: RebootStatus
fields.description: The reboot state of the VM following completion of the operation.

fields.name: StartDateTime
fields.description: The UTC timestamp when the operation began.

fields.name: StartedBy
fields.description: Indicates if operation was triggered by user or by platform.

fields.name: Status
fields.description: The overall success or failure status of the operation. It remains "InProgress" until the operation completes. At that point it will become "Failed", "Succeeded", "Unknown" or "CompletedWithWarnings."
